import React from 'react'
import NavBar from '../navigation/NavBar'
import SignUpItem from './SignUpItem'
import Footer from '../../footer/Footer'

const SignUp = () => {
    return (
        <>
            <NavBar hero='Registration' cmp='auth' />
            <SignUpItem />
            <Footer />
        </>
    )
}

export default SignUp
